1.0.10.name: wordpress/wolfnet-idx-for-wordpress
1.0.10.description: The WolfNet IDX for WordPress plugin provides IDX search solution integration with any WordPress website. To integrate WolfNet IDX data with your WordPress website, you must have a WolfNet IDX property search solution. To activate the WolfNet IDX for WordPress plugin, you must have a unique product key. Please contact WolfNet Customer Service for support via phone at 612-342-0088 or toll free at 1-866-WOLFNET, or via email at service@wolfnet.com. You may also find us online at WolfNet.com.
